You see Mr. Frank glance up from his mop. You keep your eyes straight ahead and keep moving. You'd rather not get into it.

Choices:
- Duck into the office for your coat from the lost-and-found -> hallend_nobackpack_coat_unc_wary
- Keep walking toward Mr. Bradley's room -> hallend_nobackpack_nocoat_unc_wary

