scene: sidedoor_nobackpack

The door opens easy. The air outside is warm and smells like spring and wet blacktop. Around the corner you can hear voices. Your class. Playing kickball. Right now. Without you. You don't even have your coat or your backpack, but who cares right now.

One step. Two steps.

"Hey."

Mr. Frank is ten feet away with a mop. He's not mad. He just looks patient, and very sure of himself.

Choices:
- Say sorry and go back inside -> junction_nobackpack_unc_friendly
- Slip back inside without a word -> junction_nobackpack_unc_wary
- Keep going -> badend_caught

